Code published along with my talk "Android apps in sheep's clothing"

This is an Android malware application that exploits the fact that Android has APIs to draw over the screen/display and therefore fake views. 

This Android app also works on Blackberry and can be used for the same exploit there.

References and more information:

"Android apps in sheep's clothing" on http://www.modzero.ch/modlog/index.html
http://www.sig-switzerland.ch/event_zurich4.php
(German) http://www.inside-it.ch/articles/39720
